snippet.textDisplay: It's probably quite weird having an English speaking person here, but I'm really happy you have this german version. I have lots of german relatives who I can share this with, who will definitely understand this much more than the English version. Thank you, to all the Kurzgesagt channels, for making this video in not just one, but 3 languages. I bet this has helped many people.
